edu.uml.cs.isense.credentials
Class EnterName

java.lang.Object
  Activity
      edu.uml.cs.isense.credentials.EnterName

public class EnterName
extends Activity

Allows the user to identify his/her data sets with their chosen name. This can allow for students to use a teacher's iSENSE Account, because each student will have a unique identity. The Login activity should be called before this activity.
